RE/MAX Real Estate Professionals, Inc. East Lansing

data.description: Affordable well taken care of home has many features that are rare to hit the market. Two-bedroom home with an attached garage by a breezeway/mudroom. The front porch is enclosed and is used as a three seasons room with an outside entrance. On the inside of the home, you will find a well laid out kitchen, large living and dining room.  The dining room has a sliding glass door to the large deck overlooking the fenced in back yard. A rec room in the basement and plenty of storage. Hurry to show. This one will surely not last long.
